# Mandatory Workspace Rule Checklist

- before making any code edit, run a full workspace rule checklist:
  - always-applied workspace rules
  - user rules (including CWP)
  - relevant skills and their requirements
- if a planned change conflicts with any rule, adjust the plan before editing.
- after completing edits and tests, re-run the full workspace rule checklist before finalizing.
- if any violation is found during the post-edit checklist, fix it before reporting completion.
- include a concise `rules checked` note in the final response for substantial tasks.
